WEBVTT

00:00.240 --> 00:03.408
<i>...which for Yonkers
has been a long time coming.</i>

00:07.514 --> 00:10.515
And so, for all of us,
this special day

00:10.517 --> 00:13.101
is a validation
of the city's future.

00:17.858 --> 00:20.692
We're here today to
celebrate a new beginning,

00:20.694 --> 00:22.444
a new life
of a different sort.

00:22.446 --> 00:26.164
This one for five residents
of public housing,

00:26.166 --> 00:29.084
<i>who'll be the first to move</i>
<i>into the new townhouses.</i>

00:33.874 --> 00:36.424
<i>If those five residents</i>
<i>would please come forward,</i>

00:36.426 --> 00:38.210
<i>I would like, as the
mayor of Yonkers,</i>

00:38.212 --> 00:40.629
to present you each
with a symbolic key

00:40.631 --> 00:42.714
to your new townhouse.

00:42.716 --> 00:44.466
All right!

00:52.059 --> 00:55.727
- Thank you.
- Ooh. Ooh, look at this!

00:55.729 --> 00:57.779
Thank you, sir.

00:57.781 --> 01:01.866
<i>Whoo!</i>

01:01.868 --> 01:03.451
Yes, sir.

