28:50.285 --> 28:52.485
He-- hello, ma'am.
I'm so sorry to bother you.

28:52.487 --> 28:55.238
Uh, my name
is Nick Wasicsko.

28:55.240 --> 28:58.541
I was the mayor when these
houses were approved,

28:58.543 --> 29:01.378
and I just-- I was
in the neighborhood,

29:01.380 --> 29:04.047
and I just wanted to see how
the residents were doing here.

29:04.049 --> 29:06.716
- What'd you say your name was?
- Wasicsko.

29:06.718 --> 29:09.419
Nick Wasicsko.

29:09.421 --> 29:12.589
